title: Nils Landgren Funk Unit - Teamwork 2013
description:
After nearly 3 years touring around the world with its last opus Funk For Life, The Nils Landgren Funk Unit comes back now in full force with Teamwork which, as its tittle suggests, is the fruit of this amazing collaboration and alchemy in between the members of the band. (nilslandgren.com)
